       follows="left|top"
       height="20"
       layout="topleft"
       left_delta="0"
       name="height_text_lbl11"
       top_delta="32"
       width="400"
       word_wrap="true">
        Measured in meters, the LOW value is the MAXIMUM height of Texture #1, and the HIGH value is the MINIMUM height of Texture #4.
      </text>
    <button
     enabled="false"
     follows="left|bottom"
     height="20"
